Thu Apr  9 12:25:09 UTC 2026 - Jan Engelhardt <jengelh@inai.de>

- Update to release 1.5.0
  * Added option `AsPermGroup`, which can be given to
    `SmallClassNrGroup`, `AllSmallClassNrGroups` and
    `OneSmallClassNrGroup`, to return groups as PermGroups even if
    they are soluble.
  * Added functionality to convert `IdClassNr` to IDs used by other
    group libraries (gap-smallgrp, GAP Library of Finite Perfect
    Groups, gap-primgrp, gap-transgrp, gap-atlasrep).
  * Precomputed group sizes are now stored for all groups in the
    library, and are used to more efficiently determine IdClassNr
    for a given group.

